data.description: Beautiful home in Nampa in a desirable location. Quiet location close to shopping and freeway access. This Home feature 4 large bedrooms and  space for the family to spread out. The great room features a cozy fireplace with ample space to enjoy and entertain. Master has separate shower and large soaker tub. Home features RV parking with 5 car driveway and 3 car garage.
